CustomField.description: GeoResults modeled ranking score (0-100) indicating a business's likelihood of being able to use Basic Speed (Less than 5 Mbs) DSL, Cable Modem or equivalent technology considering cost, availability and features. A high score indicates that this business is a very likely Basic Speed DSL, Cable Modem or equivalent technology user and a low score indicates a very small likelihood that Basic Speed DSL, Cable Modem or equivalent technology will be useful for this business.
CustomField.label: Basic Wireline HiSpeedInt Score
